<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.10">
<l>tārār malarkkamalat taṭañcūḻnta taṇpuṟavil</l>
<l>cīrār neṭumaṟukiṟ tiruviṇṇa karāṉai</l>
<l>kārār puyaltaṭakkaik kaliyaṉo limālai</l>
<l>ārā rivaivallā ravarkkallal nillāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For whomever masters [this] garland of words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l>With broad hands [as generous as] a rain-filled cloud,</l>
<l>About him of Tiruviṇṇakar with straight, long roads in cool fields</l>
<l>Surrounded by lotus ponds with petal-filled flowers, sorrows will not endure.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
